Program: Start the Week
Title: 05/10/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00n03zb
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 5 Oct 2009
Andrew Marr sets the cultural agenda for the week. His guests include PD James on the art of writing detective fiction, former MI5 director general Stella Rimington on her new novel, Present Danger, and former Sunday Times editor Harold Evans on his memoir, My Paper Chase. Andrew also celebrates the life and work of composer Sir Peter Maxwell Davies. Show less